This is where you put any scripts you want to add to this app.

Scripts: 
    - scinvget.py: script powering the scinvget generating command to power dashboard
    - scinvsearch.py: script powering the scinvsearch streaming command for ad-hoc workloads

Logging: 
    - Both commands log to "SPLUNK_HOME/var/log/splunk/spycloudinvestigationapp.log" and use the sourcetype "sc:investigations:log". - The SPLUNK_HOME environment variable is accessed to create the log file accordingly.

External Data (API):
    - HTTPS API endpoints are used to make the requests in both scripts. 
    - Results are retrieved and provided in search, but NO data is indexed as of version 1.0.0

Python Libraries:
    - requests: version 2.27.1 of the requests library is used as of version 1.0.0 of this app under Apache License V2.0 http://www.apache.org/licenses/



